		&lt;/div&gt;
	&lt;/div&gt;
	&lt;p&gt;North Edgbaston is a vibrant ward located in the west of the city, with a younger age profile and a smaller BAME share of the population. While facing some challenges, the community is working together to build a brighter future.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;
